<!-- Content Curation Group -->
<section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-2">
        <a href="/content-creation-working-group/">Content Curation Working Group</a>
    </h2>
    <p>
            This group solicits ideas for new SAOA content from scholars and librarians, conducts research on available holdings, and selects and prioritizes materials for Executive Board consideration. Responsibilities include:
        </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
        <li>Consulting with digital projects and archives for potential content</li>
        <li>Selecting titles for inclusion and assessing copyright status</li>
        <li>Working with other SAOA groups to support the digital resource mission</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<!-- Funding Group -->
<section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-2">
        <a href="/funding-working-group/">Funding Working Group</a>
    </h2>
    <p>
            This group advises the Executive Board on financial matters, including:
        </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
        <li>Fundraising from external sources</li>
        <li>Developing financial plans and cash flow projections</li>
        <li>Recruiting new institutional members</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<!-- Infrastructure Group -->
<section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-2">
        <a href="/infrastructure-working-group/">Infrastructure Working Group</a>
    </h2>
    <p>This group supports the technology backbone of SAOA. Focus areas include:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
        <li>Administration, staffing, and partnerships</li>
        <li>Site improvements and operational standards</li>
        <li>Digitization and metadata practices</li>
        <li>Preservation and long-term storage</li>
        <li>Project-based tasks like QA and ingest handling</li>
        <li>Adapting to emerging technology needs (e.g., images, datasets, archives)</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<!-- Outreach Group -->
<section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-2">
        <a href="/outreach-working-group/">Outreach Working Group</a>
    </h2>
    <p>This group promotes SAOA and helps shape its public presence. Activities include:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
        <li>User engagement and community building</li>
        <li>Developing sustainable outreach strategies</li>
        <li>Creating content and workflows for social media</li>
        <li>Diversifying the SAOA user base</li>
    </ul>
</section>